I"y<p>Wherever you are, I hope Spring has arrived. Yup, it’s time to shed warm coats and puffas and shop the spring jacket. While black and navy are classics and a very useful staple in everyone’s wardrobe, nothing says Spring 2019 like this beautiful, deep blue check jacket.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/verve-1/verve-2.jpg" alt="verve-2.jpg" /></p>

<p>With its gorgeous wide lapels and sophisticated button detailing, it really is a statement piece. Slightly oversized to give you a waif like silhouette, this jacket will work across every type of weather we get - either with a skinny jersey or fine knit tee underneath.</p>

