<p>The two-tone check design means you can match or contrast your bottom half: I chose my favourite high waisted style, cropped palazzo pants in deep red to pick up on the pattern and contrasted the look overall with a glossy white vest.</p>

<p><img src="/images/fashion/verve-1/verve-1.jpg" alt="verve-1.jpg" /></p>

<p>Glam up with killer heels and strong make-up or make it a more relaxed look over cropped, frayed hem jeans with flatties. Whatever you choose, I guarantee you will look amazing! Thank you <a href="https://www.verveboutique.com/" target="_blank">Verve</a></p>

